About Us
Welcome to Salty Soul Island Kitchen!
Giving all the island feels in the middle of Downtown Dunedin. Salty Soul Island Kitchen delivers fresh, affordable food, local beer, homemade sangria and good vibes in a chill and friendly atmosphere. It's where both the locals and the visitors come to hang. Live like you're on vacation!
